Description: "A set of reliable routines to ease semiparametric survival regression modeling based on Bernstein Polynomials. `spsurv` includes Proportional Hazards, Proportional Odds and Accelerated Failure Time frameworks for right censored data, it also includes bayesian frailty modeling."
